                <note rend="inline" type="source">825.00/669: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Culbertson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName> [<date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content"
                            calendar="gregorian" when="1931-07-24">undated</date>].<lb/>[Received
                        July 24, 1931—5:45 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>74. My telegram No. 73, July 24, 10 a.m. Serious clashes between police and
                    students resulting in bloodshed and situation is grave.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Culbertson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
